description.narrative: UNICEF worked towards strategic advocacy and strong external relations through support for and proactive engagement with donors, national committees, programmes, national and international media, the building of new partnerships, growing social media presence, and monthly situation reports. The net results were a successful CRC@30 advocacy campaign with buy-in high level officials, influencers, sections and field offices, private partners, and the Iraqi public, steady coverage of Iraqi children's issues and UNICEF's work in the media and donor commitment to UNICEF's multi-year programming; growing awareness of WASH issues and of the rights of children of parents believed to be affiliated with ISIL | Status:On-track | As-of Date:24/12/2018
